item.title: Ep. 176: 7 Reasons Why You Need An Automatic Savings Plan
item.description:
Achieving your financial goals takes a lot of discipline and consistency. Tune in to today's episode where your favorite Pambansang Wealth Coach Chinkee Tan shares 7 reasons why you should set up an automatic savings plan to help you reach your goals. item.title: Donna Tashjian
item.description:
Donna Tashjian

Donna is the founder of Vibrant Living International, a non-profit organization. She is a Life Mastery Coach, an ordained minister, a podcaster, and an author. She helps bring accelerated transformation to people across the world. She empowers you to master life, spirit, soul, and body. Donna has been speaking and coaching for over 25 years...
